      "span_text": "NIH-3T3 cells were grown in DMEM (4500 mg of glucose/L) with Glutamax supplemented with 10% heat-inactivated FCS, streptomycin (100 mg/L), and penicillin (60 mg/L). 3T3 embryonal fibroblasts were from SHP2 wild-type mice (SHP2-wt) or SHP2 exon 3-deficient mice (SHP2-mut) and were grown in DMEM (4500 mg of glucose/L) with Glutamax, 10% FCS, 100 mg/L streptomycin, and 60 mg/L penicillin"
